<section class="section">
  <div class="container content">
    <h1 class="title">About <%= t("app-name") %></h1>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="title is-4">What is <%= t("app-name") %>?</h2>
      <p>
        <%= t("app-name") %> is a web application for uploading and browsing <%= t("factorio-name") %> world maps captured by the
        <a href="https://mods.factorio.com/mod/mapshot"><%= t("mapshot-name") %></a> mod.
        Upload a tile set directly from your browser and share it with others,
        or explore maps that the community has shared.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="title is-4">Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Upload <%= t("mapshot-name") %> output (tile images and metadata) directly from your browser</li>
        <li>Browse maps shared by the community</li>
        <li>Interactive viewer with pan, zoom, surface switching, generation history, train station overlay, and resource tag overlays</li>
        <li>Sign in with <%= t("github-name") %>, <%= t("discord-name") %>, or <%= t("steam-name") %></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="title is-4">Built with</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Ruby &middot; Hanami 2 &middot; Dry.rb &middot; ROM.rb &middot; PostgreSQL</li>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> SolidJS &middot; Leaflet &middot; Bulma &middot; TypeScript</li>
        <li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> AWS S3 &middot; CloudFront &middot; ECS Fargate</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="title is-4">License</h2>
      <p>
        <%= t("app-name") %> is released under the
        <a href="https://github.com/sakuro/pasta_atlas/blob/main/LICENSE.txt">MIT License</a>.
        This application is built on many excellent open-source projects,
        including Hanami, SolidJS, Leaflet, Bulma, and more.
      </p>
      <p>
        Icons from <%= t("factorio-name") %> are the property of <a href="https://factorio.com/">Wube Software</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This application is built around the <a href="https://github.com/Palats/mapshot"><%= t("mapshot-name") %></a> mod by Pierre Palats.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
